item.dc:creator: @Tatemo Tatemo
item.description:
@Tatemo wrote:

[quote=“mmaKush, post:1, topic:308252”]- Spawn is in Edgeville.(1 minute max)

  • Added where if your first log-in is true; then you receive these certain items; if it’s
    not your first log-in, you get the welcome interface. (Already in there)

  • Added most of the potions; fixed a small bug with the prayer drinking.
    (Didn’t have the drinking animation added). (15 seconds not including opening the class)

  • Added conventions to the Barrows mini game class. (Already in there)

  • Edited the Item.cfg file, added my own SkillCapes and a lot of custom items but they
    weren’t shitty, all done correctly with custom bonuses and I set the prices to 1;
    couldn’t be asked to change them. . Also, they weren’t shitty items, just the new Whip,
    Helm of Neitiznot, SkillCapes (Attack, Strength, Defence, Range, Prayer, Magic, and HP),
    Better Barrows Gloves, Better Dragon Platelegs, DFS (moves with your character), a great
    Dragon Platebody, Dragon Boots, HD Dharoks Axe model, Fixed the Obsidian Maul wielding, & Dragon pickaxe.
    (Probably the most time consuming part)

  • Fixed a few bugs (Which aren’t listed)
    (Can’t really remember; maybe I should’ve wrote this down as I went along).

  • Fixed the prayer icons; they were a bit messed up. (This took a swap of two declarations in the player.java file)

  • Fixed a few weapons; not all of them were correct. (Do I have to say?)

  • Fixed some of the 2-Handed weapons wielding shields. (Do I have to say?)

  • Fixed the chins with custom models being added; they should all work now. (Do I have to say?)[/quote]
